data.text:
Astoria, OR, USA

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 46.187580, -123.834114.

Astoria is a small coastal town in northern Oregon, situated right on the Pacific shores, right on the mouth of the Columbia River. The famous Astoria-Megler bridge is located nearby, and the town is a small community which is a part of Portland area. There are plenty of truly beautiful houses and mansions in the town, like Captai Flavel House, the building of old Town High School, as well as a few modern buildings like the building of the town Maritime museum, etc.
